<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy & Messaging Terms — The Utopia Deli</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ud-primary: #590B3F;
      --ud-secondary: #754681;
      --text: #1F2937;
      --text-light: #6B7280;
      --bg: #FBFCFE;
      --card: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #E5E7EB;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Open Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ud-primary);
      margin: 0 0 8px;
    }
    .header p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .section {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--ud-primary);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .section p, .section li {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .section ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: var(--ud-secondary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="images/logo.png" alt="The Utopia Deli">
      <h1>Privacy & Messaging Terms</h1>
      <p>The Utopia Deli — 801 S. Chester St., Little Rock, AR</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>📱 Text Messages (SMS)</h2>
      <p>By providing your phone number, you consent to receive text messages from The Utopia Deli about:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Order updates and pickup reminders</li>
        <li>Weekly menu announcements</li>
        <li>Meal prep deadlines and availability</li>
        <li>Catering openings and special events</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Message frequency:</strong> 2–4 messages per week. Message and data rates may apply based on your carrier plan.</p>
      <p><strong>To opt out:</strong> Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time. You will receive one confirmation message and then no further texts.</p>
      <p><strong>To get help:</strong> Reply <strong>HELP</strong> or call us at <a href="tel:5015515944">(501) 551-5944</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>📧 Email Communications</h2>
      <p>By providing your email address, you consent to receive emails from The Utopia Deli about:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Order confirmations and receipts</li>
        <li>Weekly specials and menu drops</li>
        <li>Meal prep reminders and deadlines</li>
        <li>Community stories, events, and behind-the-scenes updates</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Email frequency:</strong> 2–3 emails per week.</p>
      <p><strong>To unsubscribe:</strong> Click the "Unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any email. You'll be removed within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>🔒 How We Protect Your Info</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Your contact info is stored securely and never sold to third parties.</li>
        <li>We only share data with trusted services (Square for payments, our email/SMS provider) to operate the deli.</li>
        <li>You can request a copy of your data or ask us to delete it by emailing <a href="mailto:theutopiadelilittlerock@gmail.com">theutopiadelilittlerock@gmail.com</a>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>📋 Contact Us</h2>
      <p>The Utopia Deli<br>
      801 S. Chester St., Little Rock, AR 72202<br>
      📞 <a href="tel:5015515944">(501) 551-5944</a><br>
      ✉️ <a href="mailto:theutopiadelilittlerock@gmail.com">theutopiadelilittlerock@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 The Utopia Deli. Built with care in Little Rock.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
